msgid "Fan chart"
msgstr "Waaierdiagram"

#: src/Module.php:234 src/Traits/ModuleChartTrait.php:46
#, php-format
msgid "Fan chart of %s"
msgstr "Waaierdiagram van %s"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/fan-size.phtml:23
msgid "Fan size"
msgstr "Waaierhoek"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/font-size.phtml:23
msgid "Font size"
msgstr "Tekstgrootte"

#: src/Configuration.php:362
msgid "Full place name"
msgstr "Volledige plaatsnaam"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:51
msgid "General"
msgstr "Algemeen"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/generations.phtml:23
msgid "Generations"
msgstr "Generaties"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/display.phtml:78
msgid "Hide empty segments"
msgstr "Verberg lege segmenten"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/page.phtml:80
msgid "Hide more options"
msgstr "Minder opties"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:65
msgid "Hide the PNG export button"
msgstr "Verberg de PNG-exportknop"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:56
msgid "Hide the SVG export button"
msgstr "Verberg de SVG-exportknop"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:102
msgid ""
"How much of each place hierarchy is shown in chart arcs (full name, or only "
"the lowest 1–3 levels). Users toggle place visibility on/off in the chart "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Hoeveel van elke plaatshiërarchie in de grafieklussen wordt getoond "
"(volledige naam of alleen de laagste 1–3 niveaus). Gebruikers schakelen de "
"plaatsweergave in/uit in het grafiekformulier."

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/display.phtml:59
msgid ""
"Images are only shown if the arc segment is wide enough. Images for "
"descendants are not yet available."
msgstr ""
"Afbeeldingen worden alleen getoond als het boogsegment breed genoeg is. "
"Afbeeldingen voor nakomelingen zijn nog niet beschikbaar."

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/page.phtml:41
msgid "Individual"
msgstr "Persoon"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/details.phtml:34
msgid ""
"Inserts the GEDCOM NICK value in quotes between the given names and the "
"surname (e.g. Martin \"Chalky\" White). Mirrors the legacy webtrees "
"behaviour for trees that store nicknames in the separate GEDCOM NICK field."
msgstr ""
"Voegt de GEDCOM NICK-waarde tussen aanhalingstekens in tussen de voornamen "
"en de achternaam (bv. Martin \"Chalky\" White). Bootst het oude webtrees-"
"gedrag na voor stambomen die bijnamen in het afzonderlijke GEDCOM NICK-veld "
"opslaan."

#: src/Configuration.php:363
msgid "Lowest level (e.g. parish)"
msgstr "Laagste niveau (bijv. parochie)"

#: src/Configuration.php:365
msgid "Lowest three levels"
msgstr "Laagste drie niveaus"

#: src/Configuration.php:364
msgid "Lowest two levels"
msgstr "Laagste twee niveaus"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/colors.phtml:43
msgid "Maternal"
msgstr "Moederlijk"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:25
msgid "Modules"
msgstr "Modules"

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/help-button.phtml:32
msgid "Move the chart"
msgstr "Diagram verplaatsen"

#: src/Module.php:262
msgid "Move the view with two fingers"
msgstr "Verplaats de weergave met twee vingers"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:74
msgid "Name abbreviation when space is tight"
msgstr "Afkorting van naam bij beperkte ruimte"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/inner-levels.phtml:23
msgid "Number of inner levels"
msgstr "Aantal binnenste niveaus"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/display.phtml:71
msgid ""
"Partners and children are shown as arcs below the ancestor section. The fan "
"size is limited to 180–270 degrees when enabled."
msgstr ""
"Partners en kinderen worden als bogen onder het vooroudergedeelte getoond. "
"De waaiergrootte is beperkt tot 180–270 graden wanneer ingeschakeld."

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/colors.phtml:39
msgid "Paternal"
msgstr "Vaderlijk"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:91
msgid "Place detail"
msgstr "Plaatsdetail"

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/center-button.phtml:18
msgid "Re center"
msgstr "Opnieuw centreren"

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/help-button.phtml:33
msgid "Reload chart for that person"
msgstr "Diagram voor die persoon herladen"

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/help-button.phtml:30
msgid "Right-click"
msgstr "Rechtsklik"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/display.phtml:65
msgid "Show descendants"
msgstr "Nakomelingen tonen"

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/help-button.phtml:30
msgid "Show details of a person"
msgstr "Toon details van een persoon"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/colors.phtml:28
msgid "Show family colors"
msgstr "Toon familiekleuren"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:119
msgid ""
"Show full dates (birth, marriage, death) for early generations. Later "
"generations show year only. Marriage dates are hidden from generation 9. "
"Descendants with narrow arcs automatically use a compact year-only format."
msgstr ""
"Toon volledige datums (geboorte, huwelijk, overlijden) voor vroege "
"generaties. Latere generaties tonen alleen het jaar. Huwelijksdatums worden "
"verborgen vanaf generatie 9. Afstammelingen met smalle bogen gebruiken "
"automatisch een compact alleen-jaar-formaat."

#: src/Configuration.php:201
#, php-format
msgid "Show full dates up to generation %s"
msgstr "Toon volledige data tot generatie %s"

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/help-button.phtml:18
msgid "Show help"
msgstr "Toon Help"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/display.phtml:55
msgid "Show images only"
msgstr "Toon alleen afbeeldingen"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/page.phtml:79
msgid "Show more options"
msgstr "Meer opties"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/display.phtml:41
msgid "Show names and images"
msgstr "Toon namen en afbeeldingen"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/display.phtml:48
