msgstr "Toon alleen namen"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/details.phtml:28
msgid "Show nicknames in display names"
msgstr "Toon bijnamen in weergavenamen"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/details.phtml:53
msgid "Show parent marriage dates"
msgstr "Toon huwelijksdata van ouders"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/details.phtml:40
msgid "Show places"
msgstr "Toon plaatsen"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/inner-levels.phtml:27
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of levels in which the text is written along an arc. "
"Descendant arcs switch between arc text and rotated text automatically based "
"on available space."
msgstr ""
"Geeft het aantal niveaus aan waarin de tekst langs een boog wordt "
"geschreven. Nakomelingsenbogen schakelen automatisch tussen boogtekst en "
"geroteerde tekst op basis van de beschikbare ruimte."

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/fullscreen-button.phtml:18
msgid "Switch between full screen mode and normal view"
msgstr "Schakelen tussen volledig scherm en normale weergave"

